Date:   2012-10-30 12:42:13 -0700

    TODO: remove accept filter/TCP_DEFER_ACCEPT item
    
    Those probably won't ever be needed point due our design.

commit 11fdd1e232fbd7657b043b3891f9638a44957ef2
