Date:   2012-03-19 13:39:47 -0700

    README: add link to the NEWS.atom.xml feed
    
    This makes it easier for subscribers to be notified of new
    releases.

commit f25b7f5cc6fc3e752e3943aa82e67a3cfdf5d21d (tag: v0.2.1)
